We compare our method with seven common FL and state-of-the-art PFL methods.
Results in Table 1 demonstrate that our FedSoup method achieves competitive performance on local evaluation sets while significantly improving generalization with respect to global performance.
Furthermore, FedSoup exhibits greater stability with lower variance of performance across multiple experiments.
